Package: stanglogitMer
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Hierarchical Generalized-Logit Model to study behavioural peripersonal space as a continuum
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Michele Scandola <michele.scandola@univr.it> [aut, cre]", 
    "Marzia Zanini [aut]"
  ))
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1), rstan
Description: This package fits Bayesian Hierarchical Generalised-Logit models.
    These models are particularly useful to study the behavioural peripersonal space
    as a continuum, by the estimation of the boudary and the stepness of the
    peripersonal space boundary.
